description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at a very elusive piece of lost media known as "Everyone Knows That", this was was originally posted on a corner of the Internet years ago and for a while these 18 seconds were unidentified, until today that is. A few researchers have traced this song back to media that we can't even show you on here! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Most Elusive Lost Song Has Just Been Found...
